ocal/20201103/AVAZRJ7AWRHZBHR77NH5QYMNAU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201103%2FAVAZRJ7AWRHZBHR77NH5QYMNAU%2F&d=fL1pPRntFf1zvvLBqslw3re6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=810af205\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201103%2FAVAZRJ7AWRHZBHR77NH5QYMNAU%2F&h=7746e454\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201103/AVAZRJ7AWRHZBHR77NH5QYMNAU/</a><br />\n<br />\n民建聯立法會議員周浩鼎今年5月在元朗朗屏擺街站，支持訂立港區國安法，其間遭人推撞肩膊。警方稍後拘捕一名男子，該男子於警誡下稱當時是為了引起周的注意，才會拍周的肩膊，並打算和周討論國安法。男子原被控普通襲擊罪，案件今午預審時，控方對被告撤控，同意讓他簽保守行為結案。換言之，周浩鼎不用以證人身份出庭作供及接受辯方盤問。<br />\n<br />\n周浩鼎回應指，同意被告接受簽保守行為，並指法律上如果受害人同意不作檢控、與被告和解，而且案情不嚴重的話，可用簽保守行為方式處理案件。周稱希望透過今次簽保守行為，給予被告改過自新的機會，「不要重犯及沉迷違法抗爭」。"},{"pid":"33e033ed0734bfec8bdd3ac04802ad242666a90d","tid":2287962,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T08:05:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ffb4de213f92b0acc6d3db07616ffa17b419c02","tid":2287962,"uid":69,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"ade67bfe1529b16b0fe2419f023c17b6e81be558","tid":2287962,"uid":282991,"like":9,"dislike":3,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T07:08:32.000Z","msg":"第一個point呢? 狗連信都唔識打?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T08:08:18.000Z","msg":"公函格式係咁的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baeaeb1b22ef820bfd70e24203e6371aee4fcad2","tid":2287962,"uid":229436,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T08:10:30.000Z","msg":"做埋ｄ仆街野<br />\n之後個政府同班狗竟然仲問我地香港人點解要做反對派點解要反政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8acc95cf56bd6e42403ebd19b76766cc5c90a819","tid":2287962,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T08:11:40.000Z","msg":"有曬live=證據不足<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img s