2,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T09:22:51.000Z","msg":"咁樣對狗又唔會變襲狗?"},{"pid":"37cdd7745e98052f8e7b1dde1b27c8eed7184818","tid":2287962,"uid":201036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e5b9ef427bff589965e34b95a950b47f8b8b6377","tid":2287962,"uid":73972,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T08:03:24.000Z","msg":"周浩鼎俾市民拍下膊頭差佬就拉人兼起訴（雖然最後簽守行為了事），而加郭偉強成個人拉跌人都話證據不足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201103/AVAZRJ7AWRHZBHR77NH5QYMNAU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201103%2FAVAZRJ7AWRHZBHR77NH5QYMNAU%2F&d=fL1pPRntFf1zvvLBqslw3re6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=810af205\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201103%2FAVAZRJ7AWRHZBHR77NH5QYMNAU%2F&h=7746e454\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201103/AVAZRJ7AWRHZBHR77NH5QYMNAU/</a><br />\n<br />\n民建聯立法會議員周浩鼎今年5月在元朗朗屏擺街站，支持訂立港區國安法，其間遭人推撞肩膊。警方稍後拘捕一名男子，該男子於警誡下稱當時是為了引起周的注意，才會拍周的肩膊，並打算和周討論國安法。男子原被控普通襲擊罪，案件今午預審時，控方對被告撤控，同意讓他簽保守行為結案。換言之，周浩鼎不用以證人身份出庭作供及接受辯方盤問。<br />\n<br />\n周浩鼎回應指，同意被告接受簽保守行為，並指法律上如果受害人同意不作檢控、與被告和解，而且案情不嚴重的話，可用簽保守行為方式處理案件。周稱希望透過今次簽保守行為，給予被告改過自新的機會，「不要重犯及沉迷違法抗爭」。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T09:24:26.000Z","msg":"姓黨犯法都冇事"},{"pid":"fc343428fecb84b66be47174b6c13f84f6077d70","tid":2287962,"uid":324034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T09:25:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12d5bc44437ec60e20b400e3131e5fdb1c404cfe","tid":2287962,"uid":44884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T09:28:26.000Z","msg":"是但啦 預左"},{"pid":"d644a6c6935e9d78f5e862970efc8a42aabd8e4b","tid":2287962,"uid":71635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-16T09:28:58.000Z","msg":"可能當場殺完人都無證據起訴<img src=\"/assets/faces/no